--------------------------
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:
--------------------------

1) Before you compile Pessoa, configure the Makefile (depending on your system):

MATLAB	       = # Root directory of your Matlab installation.
SYSTEMEX       = # Valid options: glnx86 glnxa64 mexmaci glnxa64 mexmaci.
LDFLAGS_LIB    = # Valid options: -arch i386 -arch x86_64 #-mtune=native -fPIC

2) Compile Pessoa

3) Run install_Pessoa.sh

4) Copy ./Pessoa_1.4 to your preferred folder for Matlab Toolboxes. Add to your matlab path the folder ./Pessoa_1.4

5) Now you are ready to use Pessoa. 

A sample script of a typical use of Pessoa can be found in usr/example/DCmotor.m. 
A sample of a function to generate a target set can be found in Pessoa_1.4/_template_pss_target_set.m.
A sample of a function to generate models for more complex dynamics can be found in Pessoa_1.4/usr/_template_pss_dynamics.m.

6) Enjoy!

For a tutorial on how to use Pessoa visit our web: http://www.cyphylab.ee.ucla.edu/pessoa
